# Sportfun — Environment Variables
#
# SETUP:
# 1. Rename this file from ".env.example" to ".env.local"
# 2. Sign up at: https://www.football-data.org/client/register  (free)
# 3. Copy your API token from your account profile page
# 4. Paste it below:
#
# NOTE: You can also enter the token directly in the /admin panel —
#       it saves automatically to your browser and doesn't need this file.

VITE_FOOTBALLDATA_TOKEN=your_football_data_token_here
